      "pos": [
        27,
        86
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Learn how to monitor the hardware components of your StorSimple device through the StorSimple Manager service.",
      "pos": [
        104,
        214
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Use the StorSimple Manager service to monitor hardware components and status",
      "pos": [
        494,
        570
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Overview",
      "pos": [
        575,
        583
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This article describes the various physical and logical components in your on-premises StorSimple device.",
      "pos": [
        585,
        690
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "It also explains how to monitor the device component status by using the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Maintenance<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page in the StorSimple Manager service.",
      "pos": [
        691,
        819
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Maintenance<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page shows the hardware status of all the StorSimple device components.",
      "pos": [
        822,
        913
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Under the list of components for 8100, there are three sections that describe:",
      "pos": [
        914,
        992
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        996,
        1166
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Shared Components<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – These are not part of the controllers, such as disk drives, enclosure, PCM components and PCM temperature, line voltage, and line current sensors."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1170,
        1359
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Controller 0 Components<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – The components that reside on Controller 0, such as controller, SAS expander and connector, controller temperature sensors, and the various network interfaces."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1363,
        1481
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Controller 1 Components<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – The components that constitute Controller 1, similar to those detailed for Controller 0."
    },
    {
      "content": "An 8600 device has additional components that correspond to the Extended Bunch of Disks (EBOD) enclosure.",
      "pos": [
        1483,
        1588
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Under the list of components, there are five sections.",
      "pos": [
        1589,
        1643
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Of these, there are three sections that contain the components in the primary enclosure and are identical to the ones described for 8100.",
      "pos": [
        1644,
        1781
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "There are two additional sections for the EBOD enclosure that describe:",
      "pos": [
        1782,
        1853
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1857,
        1990
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>EBOD enclosure Shared Components<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – The components present in the EBOD enclosure and PCM that are not part of the EBOD controller."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1994,
        2169
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>EBOD Controller 0 Components<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – The components that reside on EBOD enclosure 0, such as the EBOD controller, SAS expander and connector, and controller temperature sensors."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        2173,
        2304
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>EBOD Controller 1 Components<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – The components that constitute EBOD enclosure 1, similar to those detailed for EBOD enclosure 0."
    },
    {
      "content": "The hardware status section is not present in the Maintenance page for a StorSimple virtual device (1100).",
      "pos": [
        2322,
        2428
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "**",
      "pos": [
        2428,
        2430
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Monitor the hardware status",
      "pos": [
        2436,
        2463
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Perform the following steps to view the hardware status of a device component:",
      "pos": [
        2465,
        2543
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Navigate to <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Devices<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, select a specific StorSimple device.",
      "pos": [
        2548,
        2609
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Click to go into the device-level menu and then click the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Maintenance<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> tab.",
      "pos": [
        2610,
        2688
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Locate the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Hardware Status<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> section and choose from the available components (as described above).",
      "pos": [
        2693,
        2794
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Simply click an arrow preceding the component label to expand the list and view the status of the various device components.",
      "pos": [
        2795,
        2919
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "See the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>detailed component list for the primary enclosure<ept id=\"p1\">](#component-list-for-primary-enclosure-of-storsimple-device)</ept> and the <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>detailed component list for the EBOD enclosure<ept id=\"p2\">](#component-list-for-ebod-enclosure-of-storsimple-device)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        2920,
        3154
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Use the following color coding scheme to interpret the  component status:",
      "pos": [
        3158,
        3231
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        3239,
        3299
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Green check<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – Denotes a <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Healthy<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> or <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>OK<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> component."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        3307,
        3361
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Yellow<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – Denotes a component in <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Warning<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> state."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        3369,
        3464
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Red exclamation<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – Denotes a component that has a <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Failure<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> or <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Needs Attention<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> status."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        3472,
        3540
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>White with black text<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – Denotes a component that is not present."
    },
    {
      "content": "If you encounter a component that is not in a <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Healthy<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> state, please contact Microsoft Support.",
      "pos": [
        3545,
        3643
      ]
    },
    {
